Instead of grouping files by their type (e.g. controlers, directives,
services), this directory will serve as a container where files are grouped
by feature, understood as high-level sections of the application, often
corresponding to top-level routes.

Related links:
- ng-boilerplate (https://github.com/ngbp/ngbp)
- Scalabe apps (http://goo.gl/fJknAx)
